728317f-b.title: Richmond: Amboy Road - Clarke Avenue
728317f-b.text:
(1)
mboy Road (car theron right), at Captain
Roald Amundsen Plaa. The view is eastward across the
Plaga and shows the Elks Club (B.P.O.E.) at the S.W..
corner of Amboy Road and Clarke Avenue.
May 18, 1937
P. L. Sperr
(2)
A view of the Elks Club from the opposite
direction.
May 18, 1937
P. L. Sperr
